@node FAREWELL "So Long, Suckers!"
---<And it's Goodbye from him...>---


  Yes, after a year or so of updating, bug-hunting and generally tidying up
  FrillyCDPro the time has come for me to hang up my coat and call it a day.

  This doesn't neccessarily mean you'll never see another version of this
  door, it just won't be written by me - that's all.

  I've had many, many chats with Steve Clack (author of KewlCDPro) and
  tried tirelessly to get him to release KewlCDPro as FREEWARE and drop the
  Ł5.00 charge for the half-key you need to get it to work fully.
  Basically, he's not interested (in case people who paid for it complain)

  So, after MUCH soul searching, I'm releasing the source code to
  FrillyCDPro (minus Keyfile routine..... no-one has managed to crack it yet
  - not even the group that cracked Steve's 'LSD_Doors.Key')
  
  One last thing - you'll need the Amos CRAFT extension to compile it, as I
  used that to get at file descriptions.  You can find it on the AMOS FACTORY
  web site at this address: http://members.xoom.com/AmosFactory/front.html



                             @{"MAIN MENU" Link MAIN}


@endnode
